      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DODGING SHADOWS (1) crossed over from out wide last start before finishing third (24.99) at Sale in a Bottom Up - Maiden over 435m. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Can measure up this time. HAND PRINT (4) was in the minors two back (30.52) at Sandown but ran below best last time there, finishing 6th. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. FRAME ME (2) has missed the placings at her last couple but was in the money three back when second (23.66) at Horsham in a Maiden. Well placed here and can atone this time. WHATEVER THRILL (6) did a good job to finish third last time out over 300m at Healesville (17.06) in a Maiden, the second top-three finish on the trot.",
